description:
&lt;p&gt;With COVID-19 continuing to play a major part in all our everyday lives, we are expanding our capacity over the winter period and need your support to help deliver excellent care to our patients. We can offer ad-hoc shifts and/or longer-term placements through our Staff Bank, to work around your commitments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an opportunity to join an established, progressive team who work in a challenging and motivating environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our podiatry services offer care to an increasingly diverse caseload with the emphasis of work focused on the care of the General Podiatry / High Risk, Biomechanical/Musculo-skeletal conditions and Nail Surgery. Rotations in all specialisms are encouraged.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We pride ourselves on:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investing in your career by ensuing you are giving every opportunity to be upskilled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer you the opportunity working in a supported team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be passionate about delivering high quality and efficient adult community services by providing the best care to our patients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong motivational skill with the ability to teach and inspire colleagues through active demonstration of clinical practice and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work directly with a motivated Senior Management Team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Training and development,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent benefits including assistance with transport, childcare,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive pension&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health care schemes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our temporary staffing shifts are calculated hourly and paid weekly. You are paid only for the hours you actually work during any Assignment. Bank workers are paid on fixed third point based on the Agenda for Change (AFC) pay bands.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;HCAS: Inner 20% - Outer 15% - Fringe 5% (As per AfC)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Weekly pay will include: Basic pay + HCAS + 12.07% Holiday pay + Unsocial hours (If applicable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
